thread.title: Tri Nguyen
thread.title_full: Woodland Manufacturing reviewed by Tri Nguyen

author: Tri Nguyen
title: Tri Nguyen
text: We ordered laser cut acrylic lettering with a paint finish on some of the letters. The communication was excellent, and I'm glad we were able to get it done right the first time around. The final product was high quality and the color matched exactly what we wanted.
